; Multi-commodity test fixture.
; Transactions span GBP (£), USD ($), and EUR (€).
; The opening balances transaction uses one elided posting with multiple
; commodities — the key case fixed by resolve_elision().

2024-01-01 Opening balances
    assets:bank:gbp          £10,000.00
    assets:bank:usd            $5,000.00
    assets:gold                 €2,000.00
    equity:opening-balances

2024-02-01 GBP expense
    expenses:rent              £1,200.00
    assets:bank:gbp           -£1,200.00

2024-03-01 USD purchase
    expenses:software            $99.00
    assets:bank:usd              -$99.00

2024-04-01 EUR transfer
    expenses:conference         €500.00
    assets:gold                 -€500.00
